Name: raptus.securelogin
Version: 1.0a2
Summary: Provides a more secure login procedure for Plone for a defined set of groups.
Home-page: https://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/raptus.securelogin
Author: Raptus AG
Author-email: dev@raptus.com
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        Provides a more secure login procedure for Plone for a defined set of groups.
        If the user who is trying to log in is in one of the defined groups, a security
        token is generated and sent to him as a SMS (a mail to SMS service is required)
        or as an e-mail, which he has to enter to finish the login procedure.
        
